0.8a
----

- Added MSSQL dialect. Added support to persistence.dtd for MSSQL specific fields. Might be time for an XSD...
- Added override method to MSSQLDialect to support TOP with setMaxResults.
- Added "driver" configuration attribute to persistence.dtd for database element and Database class.
- Fixed bug in AgilePHP_Exception introduced in last checkin.
- Added regex to #@Id interceptor to abort for dialect classes.
- Added regex to #@Password interceptor to abort for dialect classes.
- Fixed PHP notice about missing offset in MVC::processRequest.
- Bug fix to BaseModelActionController::modelList introduced in last checkin.
- Added support for arrays to RequestScope store variables.